blurb_text: The 2004 federal election was held on 9 October 2004. In Tasmania, the elected candidates were Eric Abetz (Liberal Party of Australia - Tasmanian Division), Kerry O'Brien (Australian Labor Party (Tasmanian Branch)), Guy Barnett (Liberal Party of Australia - Tasmanian Division), Helen Polley (Australian Labor Party (Tasmanian Branch)), Stephen Parry (Liberal Party of Australia - Tasmanian Division), and Christine Milne (Australian Greens).
